Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.01,0:00:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking back on our youthful days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.32,0:00:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"I don't have many memories of those three years."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what my senpai murmured on graduation day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.70,0:00:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And those few memories centered on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, a popular idol who entered his school as a junior, one year behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever he met her, his heart throbbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Unintentionally, he saw something he shouldn't have,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and he couldn't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That made him forgetful about preparing for lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.47,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, his memories are mostly about girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he was a hard-working student,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,so I didn't expect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all boys like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting that question aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason I'm in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.17,0:01:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it all began during winter vacation, after Christmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,when I met my senpai again.
