Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai? Sanshirou-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Sanshirou-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. I was just thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have problems of your own as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As well? What's troubling you, Tomomi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it your entrance exams?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that girls my age worry about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.14,0:02:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Losing weight, blah blah, my crush, blah blah, and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,When we get together, it quickly turns into something like "The Worry Show."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried about my entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.27,0:02:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be lying if I said I'm not\N nervous about them, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, you're my tutor, and you got into Imperial University without a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you.{faith in him teaching her to do well}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.62,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Even without me, you'll do fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,May I air out this room a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke-kun's not home today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,B-By the way, I've been tutoring you for a while now,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never ever seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We used to chat like this a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time we talked was on the 19th of December.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already been a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You really have a good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He always seems to be busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Youko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw the flier for bargains too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You always ask me to accompany you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Izumi is from an upper class family, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomomi also won't buy anything that's on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She always wears expensive items.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.40,0:04:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind{going with you}, but I might choose the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! That's my favorite too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to catch a cold, so I'll call you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, got it. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You should take a bath later. I'm taking one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?\N We can bathe together, can't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.01,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Yui,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,has Ryuunosuke-kun left already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of him, before vacation he always slept until I woke him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to be busy during vacation.{false iframe}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:05:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I ironed his shirt properly. Would you tell him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind. I'll tell him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a magical mirror,\N I'd be even cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Onii-chan would...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A tight skirt was the right choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that Karen-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's Maijima Karen-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan, you're good at playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite appearances, I'm really good at crane games.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, she's so persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Can you come with me{stay with me} for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I go alone, I have trouble finding someone to play with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, secretly.{without telling my manager}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be prettier than anyone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,for the special someone I'll meet someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Azumi-chan, you're already beautiful, just the way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so sweet, Junko.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But flattering me won't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A coup d'état?!{Running away?!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pull it off someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hide{ myself} somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep insisting that I work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and they never let me go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It must be hard to be an idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be everyone's idol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be the idol of \Njust one special person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've been to an informal restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this, do I look like a normal girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think this is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you use it like that, even I'll feel pity for your camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Ryuunosuke-kun all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose he is. He went out early this morning too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's out on a date with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he dating someone from Yasohachi Academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No special reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's popular. {No wonders }He does look charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My photos are like art!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not allowed to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand if you let me take your photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There... and there, and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{just a creepy laugh}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember cleaning the swimming pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cleaning the swimming pool?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember? The boys and girls take turns cleaning the pool every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I do remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened just after I'd transferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. I still haven't received my uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they couldn't let an idol help with the cleaning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so everyone left me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you approached me and asked me, without hesitation, to help clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I felt really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.75,0:09:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That was probably when I started to be aware of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I feel a little tense talking to you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.17,0:10:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a little, but I assure you I'll forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Sanshirou-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Misako-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I really didn't see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't need to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tomomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be careful on a day like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants to see an old woman's underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.28,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,all sorts of people live in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.84,0:10:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,First and foremost, this uniform. The skirt is too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sanshirou-senpai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, no. That aside, what do you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask you \Nif anyone had passed by.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's short, with big eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,wavy hair, and she's cute too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, this "someone" is a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you were different from the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's as I expected: all men are the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.59,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, your house is really huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's called Karen's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too big for my family, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. It might be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you say it is sort of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm free right now, so it's okay, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a very important\N time for you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What if other agencies, who want to drag you down, learn about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't I decide what I do with my free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you should refrain from acting on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sanshirou-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yui-kun? Are you Narusawa Yui-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.10,0:12:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Sanshirou-senpai.\N He graduated last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He enrolled in Imperial\N University straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the talk of the school, the first student to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She's exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just in time. Why don't you join us for a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks, but I'm looking for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I have a piano lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you disturbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting straight to the point,\N you're disturbed about love, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you what the girl you have a crush on is thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.94,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, here's the result!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She has no feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's a chance that she might fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And the proof of it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.17,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,See, she's calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the work of one of my tutors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping that I can compose something myself eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have totally forgotten about the lesson, though.{she's implying that Karen had forgotten about the piano lesson}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That school uniform of yours brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! My tutor is also a graduate of Yasohachi Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one in my class wore such a short skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while. Would you like to try it on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.71,0:14:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see you in it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Karen-kun, but there's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You shouldn't do it! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.76,0:15:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your relationship with Sanshirou-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.05,0:15:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He saved me when a weirdo was bothering me this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Your expression says that you don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.73,0:15:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a hunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you become his lover, I'll totally support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! The same goes for me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.57,0:15:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you two talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But today really was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been quite a while since I enjoyed my free time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do my best again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.13,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, are you free for the rest of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.96,0:15:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could meet her again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That depends on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to be the protagonist,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to have courage and take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.84,0:16:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What an unexpected harvest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.84,0:16:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If I use these photos, I'm sure she'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.52,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I needed to take action if I wanted good photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise guys who do nothing but flirt and chase girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:16:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was really surprised,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,because you suddenly decided to rebel against your manager.{who is speaking?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did that bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just have photo shoots tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so I guess I can laze around in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hikari-san will have to look everywhere for me. That'll cause a big fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Will your rebellion be successful?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We demand free time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Onii... Oops, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to keep it a secret from Ryuunosuke-kun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, he called just now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.48,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and said he's spending the night at Akira-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you allow him to stay out at night, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-san, don't get too friendly with Ryuunosuke-kun, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, she'd be quite jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Ryuunosuke-kun's not home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, weren't you in Ryuunosuke-kun's room the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is your home too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,yet I came here{went in?} without telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Although we live together, I've only rarely talked to him in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous of {\i1}you{\i0}, Yui-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You get to live with such a nice guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.52,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll be crowded if we both get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.62,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But it'll be fun, like a school trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been longing for this.
