Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,just like a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wear that ribbon everywhere you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.55,0:18:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I love said that he likes girls who wear ribbons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.90,0:18:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.... I decided to take it off only for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously going to sleep like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I always sleep naked at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's supposed to be good for maintaining my proportions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I'm wearing my panties today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should also try that from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Why are you wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.79,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke-kun told me if I exercise wearing a skirt he can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, you're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a good, mature figure and big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.47,0:19:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They've actually become larger recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.52,0:19:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone might be responsible for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen-chan, do you have a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what I'd like to say,\N but my feelings aren't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Yui-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.79,0:19:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I do... in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lying. You're quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if someone liked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd only cause problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I love just one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought, it's chilly without PJs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.84,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.17,0:20:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been peeking at my back from time to time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not really. I just think you're really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to touch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're pretty as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You have small hips. You're more suited to be an idol than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My butt is big.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.70,0:20:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When I wear a swimsuit, everyone laughs because it makes me look perverted.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so? But I'm jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.75,0:20:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That lace is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.91,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? Today is special, because I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding. I love lace as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want something like these panties and a matching bra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to my favorite shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure it'd suit you.\N I'll choose some for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing expensive.\N I'm already broke this month.
