Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I entered his room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,we just talked, and then he sent me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth. I promise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.24,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just didn't want you to misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was never told that the shoot would be outdoors!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.83,0:21:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.88,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I told you to stay in touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. Hurry up and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask them to start after noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.81,0:21:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, Sanshirou-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan, sorry for making you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.74,0:21:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's unreasonable\N to wear a bikini in this cold weather?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Karen-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't I wait outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I'll be done soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.45,0:21:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be trouble if Hikari-san finds you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.50,0:21:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui-chan, could you give me a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The zipper's stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I going to be a sex symbol, after all?{I don't think she's refering to porn star but I guess it'll  work}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.89,0:22:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's free. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.73,0:22:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'd be an idol, \Nno matter what your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.77,0:22:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you referring to my childish appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.70,0:22:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I lied. By the way, Senpai, this is out of the blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but what do you think of Miyuki-sensei, my piano tutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I think? That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! They're all brand-name goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You could try them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will come in any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then maybe just a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.22,0:22:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. I can't help thinking about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.39,0:22:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to see her.\N That's why I came to this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's just as I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:23:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes when I listen to\N Miyuki-sensei playing the piano,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.48,0:23:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder whether she's waiting for someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Prince Charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.89,0:23:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Or someone who would change her life.
