Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are about charm, \Nand men are about courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.81,0:23:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've seen mine, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.34,0:23:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Well, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.05,0:23:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep it a secret that\N I'm wearing undergarments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,During swimsuit shoots,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not supposed to wear anything underneath, because it leaves marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are about courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.99,0:23:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Men are about courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.12,0:23:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, I must speak up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, what are you mumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, Yui-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.11,0:24:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, what's the matter? Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.14,0:24:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.76,0:24:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.90,0:24:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.15,0:24:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become pretty hot, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.48,0:24:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I despise men like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.45,0:24:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll get back what you discarded two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.82,0:24:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.70,0:24:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.12,0:24:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.37,0:24:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshirou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.54,0:24:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, please run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.25,0:24:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.51,0:24:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.50,0:24:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.42,0:24:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.37,0:24:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take her place, so let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.43,0:24:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.31,0:25:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I let you act all brave in front of a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.93,0:25:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.64,0:25:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.03,0:25:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have the strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.48,0:25:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,then don't try to protect women!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.12,0:25:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san, I-I've always...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.08,0:25:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Sanshirou-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.09,0:25:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.38,0:25:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You fainted, so I called Onii-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.88,0:25:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. I got Ryuunosuke-kun to carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.34,0:25:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks, Ryuunosuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.97,0:25:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuunosuke-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.10,0:25:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ryuunosuke-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.65,0:25:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.78,0:25:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.53,0:25:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You took such good care of Sanshirou that he's acting sulky.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:26:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He also said your skirt is too short.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.91,0:26:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm at home, no one sees them, so it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.87,0:26:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.75,0:26:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,miniskirts makes my legs look longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.97,0:26:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you're interested, I'll only wear this{skirt} in front of you, Ryuunosuke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.76,0:26:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two seem really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.39,0:26:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always good to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.85,0:26:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But they still have a long way to go before love.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.69,0:26:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to understand something.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.81,0:26:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Love does hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.14,0:26:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Sanshirou-san's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.60,0:27:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanshirou-san, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.31,0:27:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What a mysterious person.
