Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.42,0:27:38.04,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}On the morning of our first date,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.81,0:27:42.93,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}in front of the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.18,0:27:48.93,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I indecisively kept changing my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.93,0:27:54.86,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I made you wait half an hour longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.96,0:27:59.77,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Usually we joke around,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.38,0:28:04.71,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}but just holding hands and walking together
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.71,0:28:07.83,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.83,0:28:10.54,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Still, it was embarrassing too,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.54,0:28:18.76,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}so I couldn't look at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.24,0:28:23.04,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.04,0:28:29.39,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}this moment would last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.55,0:28:35.05,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish we could watch the blue sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.05,0:28:40.54,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}just like this, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.83,0:28:44.61,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.61,0:28:50.68,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}my overflowing feelings would reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.10,0:28:56.66,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I'd just like to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.66,0:29:04.50,EdE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}that I love you so much.
